author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Amadeus Capital Markets admitted to Euro Medium Term Note Programme
text:
Oct 5 Amadeus IT Holding SA :
* Unit Amadeus Capital Markets SAU admitted to Euro Medium Term Note Programme to issue debt of up to 1.5 billion euros ($1.69 billion) within Amadeus Finance BV
Source text for Eikon:
Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8873 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
